# APILagScanner - Endpoint Latency + Status Tracker

APILagScanner is a lightweight tool for identifying API bottlenecks and slow response trends.

## Features
- Status + latency logs  
- Burst detection  
- JSON / CSV export  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/40_APILagScanner.git
cd 40_APILagScanner
python monitor.py
